      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This car is ready for a complete transformation and offers a great starting point for someone who loves a hands-on challenge. While it currently requires extensive mechanical work and cosmetic repairs to be roadworthy again, it\u2019s a budget-friendly way to get your hands on a classic project or a valuable source of parts. If you've been looking for a vehicle to truly make your own from the ground up, this is the one for you!",
