    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this well-maintained vehicle offers a superior balance of performance and refinement. The interior is well-appointed, reflecting a history of careful ownership, while the mechanical systems have been vetted to ensure reliable operation. This automobile represents a significant acquisition opportunity for those seeking a sophisticated transport solution that does not compromise on integrity or road presence.",
      "price": 32800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
